          <h1 style="color:#004C45;font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin:0;text-align: left;"> A Message from Cal Poly Humboldt </h1>
          <p id="date" style="color:#004C45;font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;margin:10px 0 20px 0;text-align: left;">June 9, 2025</p>
          <p style="color:#004C45;font-size:22px;font-weight:bold;margin:10px 0 20px 0; line-height:28px">Immigration Information and Support at Humboldt</p>
        </mj-text>
